GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/pie-distribution?tipe_proses=SEWING&startDate=2026-07-01T00:00:00Z&endDate=2026-07-31T23:59:59Z

### Q-Gate Top 3 Defect + Breakdown Part (SEWING bulan ini)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/top3-defects?tipe_proses=SEWING&startDate=2026-07-01T00:00:00Z&endDate=2026-07-31T23:59:59Z&top_n=3

